nodes.text: The Kashyyyk Medal of Freedom was an award that created by the Wookiees of Kashyyyk and awarded to any individual that fought for the freedom of the planet. It resembled a bronze and gold starburst that was suspended from a silver ribbon studed with clear stones.
It was given to a spacer by Gursan Bryes in 1 ABY, for defeating Lord Cyssc Blackscale.
